Redirects to https://www.eprobe.army.mil/; Planning, Programming & Budgeting Business Operating System; CAC Required past welcome page.
New URL: http://www.g8.army.mil/organization/program_analysis_and_evaluation/;
PA&E provides Army senior leadership direct, independent analysis of programs, alternatives, and priorities to make informed decisions regarding future years planning and programming to meet Army strategic objectives. PA&E exercises overall responsibility for developing the investment strategy for the entire Army in support of the Program Objective Memorandum and the Future Years Defense Program. PA&E manages the programming phase in the Army's Planning, Programming, Budgeting and Execution process and serves as executive agent for defending the Army program to OSD.
